\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7281696 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15335670\charrsid14621123 And you said - Tadder took Betty once to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname 
